data.description: Step into coziness and comfort with this charming 3BR 3BA ranch. No HOA and conveniently minutes away from shopping and I465. You will appreciate the spacious corner lot along with a fully fenced back yard and shed for extra storage. Want to relax after a long day? Look no further with a dedicated sun room and gas fireplace for the best escape! Benefit from a peaceful mind with a 1 year roof (warranty included), 2 year sump pump, and a fully water proof basement. With the HVAC, gas water heater, and paid water softener all under 5 years old, you're ready to move in. Discover the charm and character this home has to offer!
